data.description:
Welcome to your new home in the peaceful and highly desired Ventana Lakes community! Upon entry, the vaulted ceilings give this home an airy, open feeling perfect for entertaining. Abundant natural light & spacious family room flows into the open kitchen space with cozy eat-in dining room and bay window! The split floor plan separates the primary bedroom from the two other rooms. The primary bath features a walk-in shower and closet. You'll find plenty of additional storage cabinets in the garage and low maintenance desert landscaping in both the front and backyard.
This home is perfect both for full-time enjoyment as well as a vacation home- everyone looks out for one another. Offers 4 community buildings with outdoor facilities offering many activities, lakes for non-motorized boats... , catch and release fishing, swimming pools, pickle ball and much more for your enjoyment. Move in ready!
